uk.ac.warwick.dcs.sherlock.api.common

Interface ICodeBlockGroup

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EntityCodeBlockGroup

    public interface ICodeBlockGroup
    An interface that connects two ICodeBlocks where plagiarism is detected between two files.

    This and ICodeBlockGroup are somewhat redundant with the stuff in ModelTaskProcessedResults but are easier to work with for the ReportGenerator stuff for the time being.

      • addCodeBlock

        void addCodeBlock(ISourceFile file,
                  float score,
                  int startLineNumber,
                  int endLineNumber)
        Adds a code block to the group
        Parameters:
        file - File containing the block
        score - score (o to 1) of the block within the group, eg: 1 means block exactly matches the other blocks in the group
        startLineNumber - first line of the block, [inclusive]
        endLineNumber - last line of the block, [inclusive]
